A companion piece to both the 2009 FAST & FURIOUS movie and Brian
Tyler's score (released separately), this collection presents
hip-hop, R&B, and pop tunes from the car-centric film. Standout
tracks include Rye Rye's percussive rap number "Bang" (featuring
M.I.A.), Robin Thicke's falsetto-flaunting "Bad Girls, " and Don
Omar's synth-heavy "Virtual Diva."
